text.tspan: The Smart Device Forensic Analysis Framework will serve as a valuable resource for forensic
professionals, enhancing their ability to conduct effective and legally compliant forensic
investigations on smart devices. By providing detailed guidance, training, policy
recommendations, and evaluation tools, the framework aims to address the current challenges
in the field and contribute to the advancement of smart device forensics.
